{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_11_02",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 2話 頑張る人へのエール",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――現在",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Now",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "懐かしいわね。麻奈ちゃんのバースデーライブ\nあの時、手伝うと決めて本当に良かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It brings back memories… Mana-chan's birthday live.\nI'm really glad I decided to help back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.866666619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんも喜んでくれたし、ファンの子達とも\n仲良くなれたし。あの時の一体感は忘れられないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-chan was happy‚ and I also got closer\nwith the fans. That sense of unity is unforgettable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.866666619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "俺は、遙子さんがゲストとしてステージに立つ姿も\n見てみたかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I would have liked to see you on stage\nas a guest too‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってくれるのは嬉しいんだけど\nあの頃の私はね、かなり焦っていたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad to hear you say that‚ but…\nBack then‚ I was really impatient.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.9333332856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "私よりも後にデビューした麻奈ちゃんが\nどんどん先に行っちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-chan‚ who debuted after me‚\nkept moving further and further ahead…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "なんとか追いつきたくて\nいろいろと挑戦してみたけど、全然うまくいかなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just wanted to catch up somehow.\nI tried many things‚ but nothing worked out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8288642906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "そんな時に、麻奈ちゃんからバースデーライブの\nゲストの話をもらって、凄く嬉しかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ Mana-chan invited me to be a guest\nat her birthday live‚ and I was so happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.6999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、同時に思ったの。いくらゲストとはいえ\n今の私が大切なステージに上がってもいいのかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But at the same time‚ I wondered—Even as a guest‚\nwas it okay for me to stand on such an important stage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3137868959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "例え、ステージに上がったとしても\n麻奈ちゃんやみんなに、胸を張ることが出来るのかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And even if I did‚\ncould I hold my head high before Mana-chan and everyone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.1999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……\nだからあの時、ゲスト出演を断ったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nSo that's why you turned down the guest appearance back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.1999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。そのかわり、来年までには成長して\nステージの上でお祝いするって心に決めていたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. But instead‚ I decided I'd grow by the next year‚\nand stand on stage to celebrate her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "つまらないプライドだとは思うけど\nそれでも私には、大切なことだったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe it was a foolish pride…\nbut for me‚ it was something important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.4942162878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.5999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "つまらなくなんてないですよ。あいつも\n遙子さんのことを、かっこいいって言ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wasn't foolish at all. She also said\nshe thought you were cool‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈は遙子さんの気持ちに気付いていたんだと思います\n割り切って、それでも前に進もうとする気持ちに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think Mana noticed how you felt.\nThe way you pushed forward‚ even while struggling with it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.8999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんが……。そっか、そうだったのね……\nふふ、アイドル同士、分かっちゃうのかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-chan… I see‚ so that's how it was…\nFufu‚ maybe idols just understand each other that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.9999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "……ねぇ、{user}君\nあの時の『来年』は、結局来なかったけれど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ {user}-kun.\nThat “next year” never came in the end‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "今の私なら、立ってもいいのかしら\n……今更、遅いかもしれないけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if now‚ it would be okay for me to stand on stage.\n…It might be too late now‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7333384196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことない、って麻奈なら言うと思いますよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana would definitely say “It's not too late.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.8666717052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.8666717052
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それこそ、今度の月ストのライブでもいいと思います\nゲストとして、ステージに立っても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In fact‚ I think the next Moon Tempest live would be perfect\nfor you to stand there as a guest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.1000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんのお誕生日に、私がゲストで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On Mana-chan's birthday‚ me as a guest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.6000050385,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6900.00004769999,
          "startTime": 163.5000050862
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.6000050385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.4666717052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 163.4000050862
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 163.4000050862
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね\n仕事終わりに、わざわざ付き合ってもらっちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry.\nMaking you come along after work like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.7000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、今日の予定はこれで最後でしたから\nでも、なんでここに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's fine. This was my last appointment today anyway.\nBut… why here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.9821594046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "バースデーライブの後に、麻奈ちゃんが遊びに\n誘ってくれてね。その時に、ここに来たの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After the birthday live‚ Mana-chan invited me out.\nShe brought me here then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.6666717529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "ライブが終わったばっかりだったのに\n麻奈ちゃん、すっごく元気でね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though the live had just ended‚\nMana-chan was so full of energy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.3000101725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくだから、その時に私個人で\nお誕生日のお祝いもしたんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I took the chance then\nto celebrate her birthday on my own…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.0333384196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "その時、麻奈ちゃん、言ってたんだ\n「私も遙子ちゃんにプレゼント用意するからね」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And at that time‚ Mana-chan told me—\n\"I'll prepare a present for you too‚ Haruko-chan.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.4000071207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 206.7666737873
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "お祝いのお返しに、遙子さんの誕生日にも\nプレゼントを用意する、ってことでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So she meant she'd prepare a present\nfor your birthday too‚ as a way of returning the favor?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.333340454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "私も、その時はそう思っていたんだけど、違ったみたい\nあのライブの後、麻奈ちゃんが出した曲、覚えてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what I thought back then too… but it seems I was wrong.\nDo you remember the song Mana-chan released after that live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.4666737873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 227.0667093435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "『voyage』……\n夢に向かって頑張る人への応援ソング、ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Voyage\"…\nA cheer song for people working hard toward their dreams‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.0000071207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "本人に聞いた訳じゃないんだけど、もしかしたら\nあの曲が私へのプレゼントだったのかなって思ってるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never asked her directly‚ but maybe…\nI think that song might have been her present to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.433340454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 242.1667093435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃の……焦って、前に進めてるのかも\n不安だった私への、エールだったのかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then… when I was impatient and unsure whether\nI was really moving forward… maybe that was her cheering for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.0000071207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 251.5333760101
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あの曲は、急に制作を決めたんですよ。遙子さんが\nバースデーライブの準備をしたって知った後、すぐに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ that song was decided on suddenly‚ as soon as\nshe heard you helped with the birthday live‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.633340454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "だいぶ無茶なスケジュールだったんですが、麻奈が\n言ってました。早く届けたい人がいるから、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She rushed it into production‚ despite the crazy schedule\nand said‚ \"There's someone I want to deliver it to quickly.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.533340454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 267.4000426768
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんは、きっと分かっていたのね\n私が悩んでいたことも、全部……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-chan… She must have known.\nAll the things I was struggling with…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 272.8666737873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 275.7667093435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんに追いつくって決めてからも\n麻奈ちゃんがいなくなってからも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even after I decided to catch up to her…\nand even after she was gone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 279.433340454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk025.m4a",
      "text": "あの曲には、沢山励ましてもらえたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "that song kept encouraging me so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 282.1000426768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.1667093435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 286.1667093435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk026.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君。今日はありがとうね\nここに来て、二人で話せて、気持ちが固まったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-kun. Thank you for today.\nComing here and talking with you helped me make up my mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 290.533340454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk027.m4a",
      "text": "あらためて、昨日のお返事なんだけど……\n私、ステージに立ちたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ about my answer from yesterday…\nI want to stand on stage",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 299.8666737873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 299.8666737873
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 302.7000426768
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk028.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんの誕生日に、ステージに立って\n麻奈ちゃんが私に贈ってくれた、あの曲を歌いたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "on Mana-chan's birthday—\nand sing the song she gave me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 307.1000071207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 311.5667093435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
