      "text": "ステージの上で\n麻奈ちゃんに、おめでとうって伝えたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Up there on stage‚\nI want to tell Mana-chan‚ “Happy birthday.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 313.7000071207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk030.m4a",
      "text": "わがままかもしれないけれど\n{user}君にお願いしてもいいかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It may be selfish of me‚ but…\nmay I ask this of you‚ {user}-kun?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 319.6666737873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 322.4333963552
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "任せて下さい\nアイドルの夢を実現させるのが、俺の仕事ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave it to me.\nIt's my job to make idols' dreams come true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 324.3666941324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk031.m4a",
      "text": "うん、ありがとうね\nよろしくお願いします、私達のマネージャーさん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… thank you.\nI'm counting on you—our manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 332.6666941324,
